Workflow options:
  --workflow <name>                     Select one workflow.
  --question <text>                     Ask a question.
  --context <path>                      Include one explicit context file. May be repeated.
  --include-approved-writing-samples    Include approved writing samples.
  --include-memory                      Include all approved memory files.
  --include-project-memory              Include project memory only.
  --include-writing-style-memory        Include writing style memory only.
  --include-teaching-context-memory     Include teaching context memory only.
  --include-preferences-memory          Include preference memory only.
  --include-decisions-memory            Include decision memory only.
  --include-active-priorities-memory    Include active priorities memory only.
  --include-approved-intake             Include approved intake summaries only.
  --include-intake-policy               Include the intake policy.
  --include-intake-queue                Include the intake review queue.
  --include-intake-checklist            Include the intake review checklist.
  --model <model-name>                  Pass a model name to the llm CLI.
  --dry-run                             Print the assembled prompt and do not call a model.
  --list-workflows                      List grouped workflow names and local commands.
  --show-context                        Show included file list and exit.
  --no-model                            Print a manual copy/paste prompt and do not call a model.
  --force-large-context                 Include files larger than 200 KB intentionally.
  --force-sensitive-context             Include rejected/quarantine intake files for review only.
  --status                              Show setup status and exit.
  --memory-status                       Show memory file status and exit.
  --validate-memory                     Run lightweight memory safety checks and exit.
  --intake-status                       Show intake file status and exit.
  --intake-summary                      Show intake queue counts and exit.
  --intake-diff                         Show uncommitted intake changes and exit.
  --next-intake-id                      Print the next ITEM-#### ID and exit.
  --validate-intake                     Run lightweight intake safety checks and exit.
  --preflight                           Run non-model Chief of Staff readiness checks and exit.
  --version                             Show version and exit.
  --help                                Show this help.

